{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775841042626,"sessionID":"ses_287a38ed2ffegrCZ947SUh5m24","part":{"id":"prt_d785fc01a001GzokGREh9f4Hk5","messageID":"msg_d785fa26d001OGZ1j1blz7FWE1","sessionID":"ses_287a38ed2ffegrCZ947SUh5m24","type":"tool","tool":"edit","callID":"toolu_functions.edit:23","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go","newString":"// Package v1alpha1 contains the v1alpha1 API group types for the AgentCube runtime.\n// This package defines the Custom Resource Definition (CRD) types\n// for managing AI agent sandbox lifecycles in Kubernetes clusters.\n//\n// The API group runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh provides the following types:\n//   - AgentRuntime: Represents a sandbox instance for running AI agents\n//   - AgentRuntimeList: A collection of AgentRuntime resources\n//   - CodeInterpreter: Represents a sandbox instance for running code interpretation workloads\n//   - CodeInterpreterList: A collection of CodeInterpreter resources\n//\n// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n// +versionName=v1alpha1\npackage v1alpha1","oldString":"// Package v1alpha1 contains the v1alpha1 API group types for the AgentCube runtime.\n// This package defines the AgentRuntime Custom Resource Definition (CRD) types\n// for managing AI agent sandbox lifecycles in Kubernetes clusters.\n//\n// The API group runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh provides the following types:\n//   - AgentRuntime: Represents a sandbox instance for running AI agents\n//   - AgentRuntimeList: A collection of AgentRuntime resources\n//\n// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n// +versionName=v1alpha1\npackage v1alpha1"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/o