{"type":"text","timestamp":1775841388745,"sessionID":"ses_287a38ed2ffegrCZ947SUh5m24","part":{"id":"prt_d7864fe77001OerckQwZrSobT5","messageID":"msg_d7864f459001hLkkTy0nAjnoec","sessionID":"ses_287a38ed2ffegrCZ947SUh5m24","type":"text","text":"I have successfully implemented the CRD CodeInterpreter type definition for the agentcube project. Here's a summary of what was created:\n\n## Implementation Summary\n\n### Files Created:\n1. **`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`** (8,494 bytes)\n   - `CodeInterpreter` - Root CRD type with kubebuilder markers\n   - `CodeInterpreterSpec` - Spec with:\n     - `Ports []TargetPort` (optional)\n     - `Template *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` (required)\n     - `SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration` (default \"15m\")\n     - `MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration` (default \"8h\")\n     - `WarmPoolSize *int32` (optional)\n     - `AuthMode AuthModeType` (default \"picod\", enum: picod/none)\n   - `CodeInterpreterStatus` - Status with `Conditions` and `Ready` flag\n   - `CodeInterpreterList` - List type\n   - Supporting types: `TargetPort`, `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate`, `CodeInterpreterCondition`\n   - Constants: `ProtocolType` (HTTP/HTTPS), `AuthModeType` (picod/none), `CodeInterpreterConditionType`\n\n2. **`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types_test.go`** (28,610 bytes)\n   - 25 comprehensive unit tests covering:\n     - Protocol and AuthMode constants\n     - TargetPort, Template, Spec, Status structs\n     - DeepCopy methods for all types\n     - JSON marshaling/unmarshaling\n     - runtime.Object interface compliance\n\n### Files Modified:\n3. **`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go`** - Added CodeInterpreter and CodeInterpreterList to scheme\n4. **`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go`** - Updated documentation to include CodeInterpreter\n5. **`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`** - Added DeepCopy methods for all new types\n\n### Test Results:\nAll 59 tests pass, including:\n- 34 AgentRuntime tests (from AR-001)\n- 25 CodeInterpreter tests (new)","time":{"start":1775841388742,"end":1775841388742}}}
